Modifications
-------------
The complete diff against the pinned upstream lives in vendor/yarutsk.patch.
In summary:

  scanner.rs  — Added `Comment(String)` variant to `TokenType`; emits Comment
                tokens from comment-skipping sites instead of discarding the
                text. `crate::char_traits` references rewritten to `super::`.

  parser.rs   — Added `pending_comments` field and `drain_comments()` method
                to `Parser`. Extended `Event` variants with anchor names,
                source-end-line, chomping indicator, and flow-style flags
                that the round-trip emitter requires. `crate::scanner`
                references rewritten to `super::`.

  char_traits.rs, debug.rs — Vendored verbatim aside from path rewrites and
                module-level `#![allow(...)]` directives.
